pre-install efetuado
    - caso nao tenha efetuado pre-install ($root)
        terminal
            - install pre-install
                yum -y install oracle-database-preinstall-19c
            - verificar id oracle
                id oracle: uid=54321(oracle) gid=54321(oinstall) groups=54321(oinstall),54322(dba),54323(oper),54324(backupdba),54325(dgdba),54326(kmdba),54330(racd
            - alterar senha user oracle
                passwd oracle
                    <insira a senha>
    - caso pre-install falhe, realizar as configurações
    
        # alteração de valores em sysctl.conf
            vi /etc/sysctl.conf ou /etc/sysctl.d/98-oracle.conf
                fs.file-max = 6815744
                kernel.sem = 250 32000 100 128
                kernel.shmmni = 4096
                kernel.shmall = 1073741824
                kernel.shmmax = 4398046511104
